      "pain_interference_child_angry": "In the past 7 days... I felt angry when I had pain.",
      "pain_interference_child_schoolwork": "In the past 7 days... I had trouble doing schoolwork when I had pain.",
      "pain_interference_child_sleeping": "In the past 7 days... I had trouble sleeping when I had pain.",
      "pain_interference_child_pay_attention": "In the past 7 days... It was hard for me to pay attention when I had pain.",
      "pain_interference_child_run": "In the past 7 days... It was hard for me to run when I had pain.",
      "pain_interference_child_walk": "In the past 7 days... It was hard for me to walk one block when I had pain.",
